## 📚 Quick Reference

### Common Commands
```bash
# Development
npm run dev

# Build & Type Check
npm run build
npm run type-check

# Database
npx prisma migrate dev --name migration_name
npx prisma generate
npx prisma studio

# Inngest Dev Server
npx inngest-cli dev

# Run Script
npx tsx scripts/script-name.ts
```

### Import Aliases
- `@/components` → `src/components`
- `@/lib` → `src/lib`
- `@/app` → `src/app`

### Environment Files
- `.env` - Development (gitignored)
- `.env.example` - Template (committed)
- `.env.production` - Production (not committed)

